<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Fiber-Bundles on Chen Kai Blog</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/fiber-bundles/</link><description>Recent content in Fiber-Bundles on Chen Kai Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 09:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/fiber-bundles/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>微分几何 (12)：纤维丛、特征类与物理学</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/12-%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E4%B8%9B%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/12-%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E4%B8%9B%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86/</guid><description>&lt;p>在这一系列文章中，我们从基础开始构建微分几何：流形、切空间、微分形式、积分、Riemann 度量、联络和曲率。一个反复出现的主题是&lt;strong>切丛&lt;/strong> &lt;span class="math-inline">$TM$&lt;/span>
 ——所有切空间粘合在一起形成的单一几何对象。Levi-Civita 联络是一种对 &lt;span class="math-inline">$TM$&lt;/span>
 的截面（即向量场）进行微分的规则，而 Riemann 曲率张量则测量这种微分的非交换性。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>